{
  "doc_id": "37596",
  "text": "Literature is replete with articles which put forth the use of numerous forms of bone graft materials, but there is dearth of studies that documented the use of bone graft along with plateletrich fibrin and barrier membranes in periapical surgeries [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . Survey of the existing literature revealed that there was no documented evidence of the use of an amnion membrane along with PRF and bone graft as a combination in endodontic surgery to the best of our knowledge.",
